id: pm-g2nd
title: Build idempotent AGENTS/CLAUDE pm guidance detector and writer
description: "Create the reusable logic that inspects root AGENTS.md and CLAUDE.md, decides whether core pm guidance is present, and appends or creates a stable marked guidance block without overwriting user content."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[5]: agent-ux,bootstrap,docs,init,pm-cli
created_at: "2026-05-17T08:59:13.994Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-17T10:09:16.049Z"
author: codex-agent
acceptance_criteria: "Detector reports present/missing/outdated per AGENTS.md and CLAUDE.md; writer is idempotent; existing user content is preserved; missing files are created only on explicit approval/add mode; marked block can be updated by template version; unit tests cover present, missing, outdated, absent-file, and both-file scenarios."
parent: pm-7t04
