close_reason: Idempotent AGENTS/CLAUDE guidance detector and writer implemented with unit coverage and init integration evidence.
body: "Research-backed design:\n- Scan repository root, not .agents/pm, for AGENTS.md and CLAUDE.md. Treat missing files as eligible targets only when the user explicitly asks to add guidance or approves creation.\n- Positive detection should require either a stable pm marker or a minimum set of command/workflow tokens: PM_AUTHOR, pm context, pm search, pm create, pm claim, pm files, pm docs, pm test, pm test --run, pm close, pm release.\n- Writer should append a concise marked section, for example <!-- pm-cli-guidance:start v1 --> ... <!-- pm-cli-guidance:end -->, and update only the marked block on future template-version changes.\n- Guidance content should be short enough for startup context: bootstrap, orient/search before create, claim/update, link files/docs/tests, evidence comments, linked test run, close/release, TOON/JSON guidance, and sandbox-safe tests.\n- Preserve existing line endings where practical and use atomic writes plus extension onWrite hooks if available in the chosen implementation path."
